    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >胡闹城堡-官方群：942605420 !</h2><br>《Feudal Friends》是一款兼具竞争性和合作性的塔防游戏。每个玩家在塔内都有不同的任务，他们试图通过创造新士兵来占领敌人的塔。作为一名指挥官，你必须决定你的塔和士兵生产的策略；作为一名铁匠，你必须为你的士兵制造武器；作为一名军械师，你必须为你的士兵制造盔甲；作为一名工程师，你必须升级你的塔，并管理好你的钱。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在线/本地联机玩家疯狂</h2></strong><br>在网络联机模式下，你们必须通力合作才能获胜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/6ee77aa9dff4f58fc2655e47fae7692c.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>给你的朋友搞破坏！</strong></h2>在紧着刺激的生产阶段扇你的朋友一巴掌，让他们抓狂！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/39c738185028661094938d0d9a03fafd.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/39c738185028661094938d0d9a03fafd.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/39c738185028661094938d0d9a03fafd.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>基本玩法</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>塔内的快速生产非常重要；使用WASD移动，并使用O和P与物品交互。<br></li><li>注意升级，变得比对手更强大；您必须在资源开发和生产制造之间保持平衡。<br></li><li>你可以在每场游戏中开创不同的策略；符文决定你的游戏策略，作为一个团队一起行动，用符文引导你的游戏策略。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/845d4dbf510ae07c73c9213e1e1e4d62.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=141 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/1487f6ff14795026b9d7003b11330a5f.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/1487f6ff14795026b9d7003b11330a5f.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/1487f6ff14795026b9d7003b11330a5f.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>作为指挥官，你要决定生产计划。分析来自敌方塔的敌人，制定好你的生产计划！<br></li><li>敌人距离太近了吗？用塔上的防御武器攻击他们！<br></li><li>你的军队需要支援吗？上战场，赐予他们力量！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/e21377934abd10c84113a7077c78b1bc.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=141 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/ba851b05515b2f7b749afe4ee25b4345.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/ba851b05515b2f7b749afe4ee25b4345.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/ba851b05515b2f7b749afe4ee25b4345.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>作为工程师，你决定如何升级。加快生产、改进原料将帮助你更快地生产士兵，使他们更强壮！<br></li><li>别忘了支持塔内的生产。为骑兵训练马匹，为步兵制造盾牌！<br></li><li>你能控制攻城武器。别忘了研究投石机来占领敌人的塔！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/eabe9625e2db5d035c784c7bcc3bde63.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=141 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/cff457bbda41bab894970b21cc01e6a1.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/cff457bbda41bab894970b21cc01e6a1.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/cff457bbda41bab894970b21cc01e6a1.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在铁匠角色中，你将为你的士兵生产武器。步兵配剑，弓箭手用弩！<br></li><li>熔化原料，倒入剑模，冷却，用铁砧使其锋利。武器就准备好了！<br></li><li>为了让你的士兵更快出塔，你应该与武器师协调，快速完成生产。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/d90d1f459951f16646b46e4ab3b84766.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=141 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/87cd0bbdf3cd0a038040c3b872ad475b.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/87cd0bbdf3cd0a038040c3b872ad475b.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/87cd0bbdf3cd0a038040c3b872ad475b.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在军械师的角色中，你将为你的士兵制造盔甲。所有士兵都想要盔甲！！！<br></li><li>熔化原料，倒入盔甲模具，冷却，在铁砧上加固。接着你的士兵就可以出发了！<br></li><li>为了让你的士兵更快出塔，你应该和铁匠协商，快速完成生产。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>将错误制造或部署的士兵送入炼狱！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/d922cde9e573b952b6f2739de47c92dc.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/d922cde9e573b952b6f2739de47c92dc.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/d922cde9e573b952b6f2739de47c92dc.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>",
